    <label>Scutiger Shieldbearer</label>
    <description>Unit Archive: NCL-12 "Scutiger Shieldbearer"
Origin: NCL "Iron Law" Heavy Support Series

This heavy mechanoid functions as a mobile shield platform, deliberately devoid of offensive weaponry. Core defense relies on integrated heavy-energy barriers capable of neutralizing diverse ballistic threats.

Primary functionality involves manufacturing shield drones in situ by consuming pre-loaded steel reserves (50 units per drone). These autonomous units feature compact barrier projectors with distinct operational parameters:
◆ Fragile chassis but exceptional shield efficiency
◆ Provides energy protection for self and allied units
◆ Automatically forms defensive perimeter around host when not threatened
◆ Delivers immediate shield reinforcement to frontline units during combat

All manufactured drones maintain dynamic defensive formations around the host unit during standby operations.</description>
